{
  "stem": "16503.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they transferred me from the, from the big hospital, and I was in, in the hospital at, at Ekron, which had its own section for their own people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had some injuries there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Believe me, there was quite a-- quite injuries, which we had to oversee.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were two surgeons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I learned an awful lot there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, Israel is full of us-- the survivors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They are dying off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, people were not ready to speak and talk about this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were not ready to listen or talk about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our main aim in life was, the war is over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Close the door, and let it be.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Start life from scratch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's precisely what I did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the long [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] run, it's wrong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You shouldn't close doors on something so terribly shocking and walk away from it, because it will haunt you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm sure, if the knowledge they have got now-- the psychiatry knowledge and psychology knowledge-- it wouldn't happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They would debrief you, as they call it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there was not, not a thing like that in existence.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Therefore, what you did-- you picked up, and you went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was precisely what I've done.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was fortunate enough to pick-- to have a man next to me who didn't go through it, who was educated, who had the knowledge of-- oh, he was young, and I'm sure, to me, he was-- he knew it all.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But he didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But to me, he did, at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was fortunate enough to, to start from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that was a wonderful thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Holy Jesus, how many tapes?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
